e season. Never will an overpowered ability stick around for weeks or months. We won't get this right every time, but by moving quickly here we hope to keep things as balanced as possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In addition to balance updates, there are planned major content patches which will include features such as new Titans, new maps, and new cosmetics.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460550/extras/gif5.gif?t=1738439220\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Absolutely No RNG</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In Ring of Titans we take the &quot;No RNG&quot; policy to an extreme. There's absolutely no RNG in anything, no crits, no random movement, no resists or uncontrollable misses. When you win, it's because you played better than your opponent, not because you got a lucky crit.</p>","developers":["Mash"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"},{"description":"Free To Play","id":"37"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1460550/header.jpg?t=1738439220","is_free":true,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257066574,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257066574/movie480.mp4?t=1729530383","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257066574/movie_max.mp4?t=1729530383"},"name":"Ring of Titans 1.0 Release Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257066574/0a95b79416ea0d97c178e30f2fd1ddd4e64c1d72/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1729530383","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257066574/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1729530383","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257066574/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1729530383"}}],"name":"Ring of Titans","package_groups":[